@startuml
title PlanPal - Component Diagram

package "PlanPal iOS App" {
  component "SwiftUI Views" as Views
  component "ViewModels" as VM
  component "Domain Models" as Models
  component "EventService" as Service
  component "Local Persistence\n(UserDefaults/JSON)" as Storage
}

Views --> VM : user actions / bindings
VM --> Service : calls
Service --> Models : create/update entities
Service --> Storage : load/save
VM --> Models : reads state

@enduml